text: Brand new home in a desirable location with 3 beds, 2 baths and just shy of 1, 500 sqft. This home features a gas fireplace in the open concept living room, a good sized dinning room with lots of natural light attached to the large kitchen w/ an island with plenty of space for entertaining. The primary suite has an attached bath with a double vanity and walk in closet. An oversized laundry room with a utility sink attaches the garage to the house. East facing back yard with large covered patio and mountain views.

WELCOME TO BALFOUR VILLAGE PHASE 2! Affordable living, JUST COMPLETED rambler in a newer community. This home features a large lot with open floor plan. 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths, 3 car garage, stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops & A/C. Come enjoy tranquil living with peace and quiet and natural surroundings. Only 30 minutes to Bellingham!

Large, tranquil and private - 0.44 Acre lot with mature Douglas Fir trees located in the heart of Point Roberts. Approximately 83' x 230' in size with good soils for septic. Lot of room for large home and shop or just have a rustic cottage tucked away in the woods. Large shed already built ready for your storage needs.

Beautiful mid county home on large commercially zoned lot ready for the master gardener all the way to business owner! This home has been tastefully updated both inside and out. Stunning finishes, new flooring, paint, kitchen and bathroom makes it a turnkey move. Three large bedrooms and a huge great room off the back. This great room is perfect for entertaining, and gatherings with a wood fireplace, floor to ceiling glass doors and peaceful views to the back yard. Unique location and zoning makes this the perfect forever home or grow your business. Large .70 ac lot is ready for a huge shop just north of the house. New roof and exterior paint. Attached 2 car garage as well as a separate shop garage for all your tools a toys. Original owner

Over $40, 000 in recent price reductions!! Irreplaceable at this new price! Great opportunity to own a larger home on a large lot with revenue potential! 4 bedrooms plus 2 & 1/2 baths. Fully equipped & private entry 1 bedroom suite on the lower grade level with shared laundry access. The suite has large windows and is bright. Open concept with high vaulted ceilings & skylights add tons of natural light on the main floor along with a dining area and 1/2 bath. 3 large bedrooms on the middle floor along with another private entrance. Lots of deck area & extensive use of wood throughout. Spotlessly clean & very solid construction throughout plus a metal roof for low maintenance. Completely remodelled kitchen plus a new septic system in 2015!

This custom-designed single level 2, 487 sqft home epitomizes elegance and functionality, perfectly blending open-concept living with the serenity of nature. Vaulted ceilings amplify the sense of space, drawing attention to a dream kitchen that offers stunning bay views through a picturesque window. With 4 cozy bedrooms and 2 modern bathrooms, it comfortably accommodates guests. The home's crown jewel is its outdoor entertainment area, complete with a hot tub (negotiable), set against the tranquil backdrop of a private greenbelt. Nestled on a generously sized lot, this property promises an unparalleled living experience, where luxury meets the peace of the outdoors. Ideal for those who cherish both sophistication and privacy.

Beautiful custom home w/ outstanding views of the ocean, islands, and sky. This meticulously maintained four seasons home offers 3 beds + den, 3 baths and has beach access. Featuring an elevated open main living area with vaulted ceilings, and large windows for beautiful light. High-end details including, maple hardwood flooring, updated appliances, custom millwork, granite countertops, stone fireplace w/ double sided propane insert and custom window coverings throughout. Enjoy a cup of tea on the east deck for the sunrise, or a cold beverage on the large covered balcony to watch the sunset and feel the ocean breeze. Beautiful gardens, professionally done and a sprinkler system for easy maintenance. Marina access just around the corner.

Welcome to your charming oasis in a prime location! This meticulously maintained home boasts a host of modern updates, including a newer roof, furnace, heat pump, water heater, and stainless steel appliances, ensuring both comfort and efficiency. Step inside to discover a cozy living space, complete with a delightful gas fireplace and waterproof Pergo floors. Downstairs, a versatile living area offers additional space for relaxation or entertainment. Outside, the easy-care landscaping that can be enjoyed from the upgraded Trex deck. Situated close to all the amenities Bellingham has to offer, this home is a true gem. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!

If you have found it hard to find a single family home in a 55 and over community then you need to come see this beautiful home in Bryce Park. It features a private location with nice covered patio, dog run or room for a garden and small yard. The interior features an open floor plan, solid surface counters, hardwood floors, gas fireplace, private utility room, private master suite, the 3rd bedroom would make a great office. The upper level features a large room that could be used as bedroom, craft room, family room or an additional office. The home features custom blinds throughout and air conditioning. This community features a beautiful clubhouse with patio and common lawn area. This home is ready to go, please come take a look

Raspberry Ridge Golf Course home on the 6th fairway. Quality built single-level home, 2 bedrooms, or use the office/den as a 3rd bedroom. Spacious kitchen, abundant cabinet space, walk-in pantry. Great floor plan connecting kitchen, family, dining and living rooms, ideal for entertaining. Primary suite features generous closet space, double vanity, tile flooring and tile walk-n shower. Stay comfortable year-round with ductless heating/AC. Expansive concrete patio, large private backyard extending to the golf course. Outdoor irrigation, beautiful mature landscaping, fresh exterior paint, an oversized 4-car garage with workbench area and ample storage. Located on a serene dead-end street, this property is a must-see!

Welcome to River-Walk, a unique NW Washington community offering attractive design, luxurious finishes & pedestrian-friendly connectivity to Lynden. Residents can walk or bike a few blocks to downtown Lyndens quaint restaurants and stores, located less than two hours to Seattle, Vancouver, B.C., Mt. Baker and the San Juan Islands. Lot 39 is located in River-Walk East. It offers a comfortable 1731 sq. ft. with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms & many upgrades. The gourmet kitchen is highlighted by quartz countertops & islands with full waterfall drops.

Fantastic opportunity for multi generational living in one of Blaine's core neighborhoods 3 bedroom/2.5 bathroom, efficient, quality built Craftsman features a functional open living, dining, a custom kitchen with huge island & stainless steel appliances. Permitted detached accessory dwelling (DADU) generously sized 2nd floor studio with a full size kitchen & a 3/4 bath large closet. This is the ideal scenario to work or school from home you decide! Detached 2 car garage, fenced back yard, patio, gardens & fruit trees. Excellent walkable location to the downtown restaurants, shopping, the waterfront & the schools...this is the one you've been waiting for. A great property for those looking to live comfortably

Impeccably maintained single level home in highly sought after Sable Terrace neighborhood. Move-in ready w/ fresh exterior paint, new fencing + updated flooring & lighting. In the kitchen, a newer refrigerator, microwave, & dishwasher with upgraded wood grain kitchen countertops for a modern touch. Roof was replaced in 2014, and under the home you will find a fresh vapor barrier + insulation. Attached garage & backyard shed offer plenty of covered space for storage or hobbies. The generously sized fully fenced backyard invites outdoor gatherings and leisure activities. Serene living on a quiet cul-de-sac, just steps away from the park and playground. Conveniently located near schools and with an effortless commute to Bellingham and Lynden.

Excellent main level condo in the heart of active Bellingham. This condo features all new carpets throughout the home w/an easy flow layout. Enter in the condo to the main living room/area, that is open to the kitchen that features an island & plenty of easy storage & pantry. The bedroom features a sliding glass door to the cozy patio opening up to a grassy area, as well as a complete custom closet system installed to maximize closet space. The bonus room also has a door leading outdoors as well as beautiful landscaping that is visible through the window. The primary bath offers even more closet space & a large vanity & wall length mirror. You won't want to miss this lovely home!

Experience nature, beauty, and impressive craftsmanship in the desirable Geneva neighborhood, gated Lost Creek Lane. Nestled up to 150 plus acres of lush public land, this home is perfect for enjoying privacy & the PNW at its BEST! Featuring a multi-tiered outdoor living area, sport court, and easy access to Galbraith Mountain trails out your front door, plus stunning Lake Whatcom. This home is situated on over a 1/2 acre lot, taking privacy to the next level. Inside you will be greeted by a spacious living room, plus a large lower level rec room, both accompanied by cozy fireplaces with beautiful wood and stone surround. Offering 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, hardwood floors and a large kitchen complete with updated appliances and walk-in pantry.

BRAND NEW!!!! One-of-a-kind, 2 bedroom cottage in the Sunset Village neighborhood is one you won't want to miss! Featuring an open concept first floor living space & kitchen that includes quartz countertops and SS appliances. A powder bath and back patio finish out the first floor. Upstairs includes two good sized bedrooms and a full size bathroom. This cottage comes with a designated parking area & a private storage unit for bikes, outdoor furniture or any other storage you may need. Call today if interested!

Lynden Gem! This Lynden home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.25 bathrooms.The generous primary bedroom features a double sink and walk-in closet. Enjoy a finished basement with extra living room/ play room. Situated on a large corner lot, relish the fully fenced backyard, a 2-car garage, a new deck (2023) plus a tool and garden shed. This home offers unique functionality in an ideal location! Close to schools, parks and walking distance to town amenities!

First time on the market in over 50 years, this classic lodge style home will wow you w the open beam ceilings, wall of windows and huge deck overlooking the valley. 3 BR 2.5 BA 2, 000 s.f. finished + 1, 120 s.f. unfinished daylight basement for added opportunity and enjoyment. Pre-inspected w a new roof & gutters, water treatment system, drainage and more. Huge 3 bay shop w an enormous loft that could be an office, guest room or whatever you can imagine. All of this on 7.5 acres w pear, apple & cherry trees, mature landscaping and room to relax, camp, play or enjoy the scenic beauty and nature surrounding this amazing property.

Experience front-row living from this top-floor Rip Tide condo that has unobstructed views of Bellingham Bay, San Juan Islands, and the Canadian mountains beyond. Just a short walk to Fairhaven and the ever-so-popular Boulevard Park and Taylor Dock. Very sought-after property as these top-floor units don't become available very often! It features a large covered deck built for entertaining and a spacious open floor plan with a large living room, dining area, and open kitchen. Exterior and landscaping were recently renovated (over 2M) with new modern finishes and there's 1 covered parking space included near the walkway and a storage unit. Walk or ride your bicycle to downtown Bellingham and Fairhaven on the trails along the waterfront.

Stunning Richmond design home situated on a spacious sunny corner lot. Recent remodels including upgrades such as LVP flooring, lighting, large oversized kitchen island, granite counters, subway tile backsplash, cabinets w/ under cabinet lighting, bathroom flooring & vanities & modern style window treatments. Enjoy the elegance of the beautiful wood aesthetic touches and the convenience of a gas range. Featuring a bonus gym space upstairs, perfect for fitness enthusiasts. Additional highlights include new int & ext paint, large backyard patio & new fencing. With its ideal location near the best Birch Bay beaches & retail, this home offers coastal living with an easy commute to Bellingham & the border. Don't miss out!

Immerse yourself in the essence of Bellingham living with this thoughtfully designed 1958 square foot home on Sussex Dr. Built in 1996, this residence offers three bedrooms and three bathrooms, combining comfort and style effortlessly. Step into the inviting atmosphere featuring two fireplaces and the airy openness of vaulted ceilings in the living area. With a three-level layout, including a main floor primary suite boasting an ensuite bath with radiant heated floors, luxury and convenience are at your fingertips. Outside, enjoy the tranquility of three decks, a hot tub, and easy access to Barkley neighborhood amenities, including shopping and scenic trails. Don't let this opportunity slip away to make this your ideal home!

Estate sale. Welcome to Sealinks, a gated community in Birch Bay. This home built in 2001, is a one owner home, single level & amazing. Clean, neat, bright with excellent sun exposure. 1287 sq. ft, 3 bedroom, 1.75 baths, 2 car garage on a 6035 sq ft. homesite. New Roof, gutters and exterior paint summer of 2023. Hardi siding, with large covered front porch, as well as spacious back deck in parklike setting. Home has natural gas forced air heat, natural gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings in the Great room concept. Enjoy the newer appliance package complete with washer and dryer. This development has front and back gates with access to the heart of Birch Bay including restaurants, beach access, new walking berm and community park. Nice location.

Trees, privacy, and brightness - hard to find in one property but your search is over. Just an exquisite home layout for a one-level county home minutes from town. You will appreciate the large large primary w/ ensuite, 2 guest bdrms, dedicated laundry space w/ sink, mud room, enclosed porch, vaulted ceiling in Great room, dining room, and 2 car garage w/ generator hookups. In addition the property enjoys a wide sunny building envelope with tall, beautiful, high-limbed evergreens. The large 48'x36' & 32'x36' shops have compartmented spaces, one w/ woodfired heater. Two additional outbuildings for use as well. Private well with filtration for the home, and a shared well for irrigation.

Sweet Sudden Valley Single Story! Built in 2003, 3 bd/1.75 bath, skylights, cement plank siding, new carpet & interior paint, move-in ready! Double pane windows, well insulated and affordable high efficiency gas heat. New walk-in shower. 2 spare bedrooms. Big open kitchen with dining area and lots of cabinets and storage. All appliances stay. Vaulted ceiling in spacious living room with cozy gas fireplace. Covered porch in front and enclosed deck in back. 2 car attached garage. EZ access from Lk Louise Dr, 15 minutes to town. Sudden Valley amenities include 18 hole golf, pool, clubhouse, strip mall, walking, biking, Lookout Mtn trailhead, kayaking, water sports, Lk Whatcom beaches & marina. Great investment and priced to sell!

Welcome to this charming single-level home, a perfect blend of comfort and style spanning 1, 500 square feet. Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this residence offers an inviting ambiance and thoughtful design throughout. Home offers newly painted interior walls, new carpet in the primary bedrooms, newly installed gas range and refrigerator, furnace recently serviced, and the air ducts cleaned. With the perfect open floor plan for entertaining and a patio with a view of the mountains, come see this quality home!

Spectacular views of Bellingham Bay!!! The mature lot lends to a tree house like feel featuring breath taking sunsets. The large living and dining room highlight the incredible views and feature original wood ceilings and large windows. The primary bedroom, with en-suite, is on the main level for ease of access. The lower level has an additional living room space and lots of storage as well as two bedrooms and a full bathroom. Recent upgrades include: high end vinyl plank waterproof flooring in the kitchen and entryway, new carpet in the lower level and primary bedroom, and fresh interior paint. There is level covered parking and room for up to 3 vehicles. You're just minutes to Fairhaven, Boulevard Park, and downtown Bellingham!

A single-level 1, 689 sqft home that has it all! Located in a quiet North Bellingham neighborhood this 3 bd / 2.5 bath home is move-in ready and will impress you with all the extras: a bright sun room, A/C throughout, covered patio, updated kitchen, bonus heated flex space, gas fireplace & 2 backyard sheds. Stretch out and enjoy the large 10k SF lot that features garden beds, a fully fenced backyard & plenty of parking. You're minutes from Costco, Ferndale, Bellingham & I-5. Come see this gem in person before it's gone!

Want to retire and downsize, but everything you look at feels too cramped? This 55+ condo just might be the ticket! One of the largest units in this bright and sunny community (1, 835sf) this home allows you the space you deserve. It is rare to find a single level DETACHED home that boasts 3 bed/1.75 bath AND 2 car garage. Guess what? You don't have to worry about the lawn, roof or painting the exterior. All the outside maintenance is budgeted for and included in the HOA and also includes earthquake insurance, cable tv, water and sewer. Enjoy strolling around the loop with friendly neighbors, playing cards in the clubhouse and the quick drive/walk to local restaurants, clinics, parks and shopping.

Better-than-new, single-level home in beautiful East Lynden! Enter to a bright & open great room perfect for entertaining, including a stunning kitchen with oversized island, quartz counters, and stainless steel appliances. Dining room opens to covered patio & level, fully fenced backyard ideal for barbeques and lawn games. Thoughtfully designed layout throughout this home, with 2 large bedrooms, utility room, and bathroom located on one side of the house and generous primary suite and dreamy primary bathroom/walk-in closet on the other. Enjoy all that East Lynden has to offer including walking trails, foothill views, and close proximity to schools.

Your dream coastal getaway awaits! Take in awe-inspiring views of majestic Lummi Bay & Mt. Baker all from your private, low bank, waterfront oasis with 59' of beachfront. Your thoughtfully designed living space includes soaring ceilings, AC, and an expansive garage with bonus work area. Transition seamlessly from indoor to outdoor living with direct access from your primary bedroom or living room to discover an outdoor entertainer's dream, complete with dining table for 10, bistro lights, and a beautiful hot tub. Sip coffee as you watch the sun rise over the bay and enjoy a glass of wine as you catch sunsets to the west from your second floor balcony. Enjoy community amenities such as the pool, golf course, and a marina. This is the one!
nearby_schools: Ferndale School District, Lummi Elementary School, Lummi High School

text: Builders and Investors come see this Vacant Land in Blaine, WA. 7, 993 sq. foot residential lot. Corner Lot.

Discover the charm & quiet of Sumas River Estates in Everson. This 3-bed, 2-bath home offers an open living space, abundant natural light, and a wood-burning fireplace. The primary suite features a spa-like bathroom and walk-in closet, while the dining room opens onto a private back deck. The functional floor plan separates the sleeping space to separate ends of the house. Freshly painted in 2019, new hot water heater in 2024, this home has been gently lived in and well maintained. Located in a gated 55+ community is close to restaurants, parks, and schools. Embrace a tranquil lifestyle in this inviting home.

Early 1900s craftsman located in the best part of Historic York Neighborhood! Nelson's Market is just around the corner and Downtown Bellingham is only a few blocks away. Original character abounds including hardwood floors, picture windows, tall ceilings, built in features, trim & loads of charm. Spacious living room with a gas fireplace is cozy and welcoming. Dining area off of the kitchen is filled with natural light. Two spacious bedrooms on the main floor and one upstairs with additional loft space. The large unfinished basement adds ample storage space and an additional half bath. Backyard is fully fenced for your privacy and there's additional alley parking for you and your guests.

This well cared-for '08 Breckenridge Park Model & gazebo comfortably sleeps 7 adults. Vaulted ceilings, electric fireplace & full size appliances are just some of the features that make it feel like home. Beautiful, gated covered deck w/ skylights provides for year-round enjoyment of the outdoors. The thoughtfully designed lot is fully fenced & backs up to greenbelt offering privacy & is just steps from Gorge Trail. There's also a covered BBQ area & wood shed. Amenities include Nooksack River access, two pools, tennis & basketball courts, playgrounds, parks, trails, disc golf, 24/7 security & more. No rentals. Occupancy is limited to 120 days/year.

Experience world-class views of the San Juan Islands from the front row of Madrona Pointe, arguably the most coveted enclave of Edgemoor. Privacy beckons you throughout the shy 3/4 acre lot of winding gardens, decorative trees & lush lawns. Oversized 3-car garage with breezeway & custom wood doors. Explore Clark's Point steps away from your door or stroll down to Fairhaven Village.

Welcome to your dream home! Introducing our exquisite new 2-story Bluff floorplan featuring 3 beds & 3 baths. The primary suite is a true haven, boasting a lavish 5-piece ensuite and a huge walk-in closet, providing ample space for all your needs. The lower level boasts a bonus room with fully tiled shower and optional wet bar. Luxury abounds with ceramic tiles, custom hickory-stained cabinets, and high-end appliances in the chef's dream kitchen. Proximity to golf clubs, Semiahmoo, Vancouver BC, and Seattle. Indulge in the epitome of elegance and coastal living. Your perfect oasis awaits.

Room for all of your toys! Fantastic location in Birch Bay for a storage condo with improvements. Gated and secure complex. Backyard Buddy auto lift included up to 7, 000 lbs. Super clean and ready for you!

With its idyllic setting and array of amenities, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and leisure that's truly unmatched.

Turnkey One-Level Home that Lives Large on Barkley Hill! Vaulted Ceilings. Cherrywood Hardwood Floors. Sunny & Bright! Gas Heat, Tankless H20, Large Fenced Corner Lot! Over-sized 2-Car Garage. Fenced Backyard, Patio & Gazebo. Working Hot Tub!

Stunning 4-plex in the heart of Ferndale! This beautiful building is only 5 years old and a great investment. Each unit is a huge 1, 560 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms. The layout is fantastic! Each unit is 2 levels. The main level has your kitchen, living room w/natural gas fireplace, powder room and deck. Then you either go upstairs or downstairs, depending on the unit, to your 3 beds, 2 bath, and washer & dryer. A perfect design for quiet nights rest with the separation of bedrooms. Building is fully leased boasting a self managed CAP rate of 5.63%! Look at the rents, there is defiantly room for an increase per unit. Seller currently pays water & sewer but units are separately metered w/another opportunity to make the CAP rate soar!

Introducing this charming 3-bed, 1.75-bath home featuring brand-new roof and gutters! The large country-style kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and stunning granite countertops. Enjoy the inviting open floor plan, ideal for hosting gatherings. Conveniently located near trails, parks, Lake Whatcom, restaurants, schools and shopping.

The list goes on... Thoughtful drought resistant landscape on drip lines, & deer protected garden w/ raised beds & potting/wood shed. Circular driveway! A Must See!

This home, the Alder plan, is a 1527 SF, 2BR, 2.25BA, 2-car garage home w/a spacious great room, open kitchen w/eating bar, quartz countertops, white cabinet package w/soft-close doors & drawers, water-resistant planked flooring, nine-foot ceilings on the main, primary suite w/luxury bath, & convenient upper floor laundry. Custom-designed home featuring stunning pond & Mt. Baker views. Enjoy a one-level living design w/ spacious living room, vaulted ceilings & built-in storage. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood with walkable trails and conveniently close to the new High School.

Step into your dream home! Nestled in one of Bellingham's premier neighborhoods, this captivating 4bd/2.25ba abode beckons you. Enjoy the ease of single-level living! The inviting living room boasts vaulted ceilings, fireplace & windows flooding the space w/natural light.
